### Test Reports API Endpoints
### Make sure to have a valid token from login

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4001/api
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Daily Summary - Today
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/daily-summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Daily Summary - Specific Date
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/daily-summary?date=2025-08-01
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Weekly Metrics - Current Week
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/weekly-metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Weekly Metrics - Specific Week
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/weekly-metrics?startDate=2025-07-29
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send Daily Summary Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/send-daily-email
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientEmail": "test@example.com",
  "date": "2025-08-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Export Consultations CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export?type=consultations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Export Students CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export?type=students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Export Weekly Metrics CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export?type=weekly-metrics&startDate=2025-07-29
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}